This document lists the hardware and connection used for creating and testing this project.

Harware
Teensy LC
RobotDyn Light Dimmer Module
HC-05 bluetooth module
DS3231 RTC module
Push button


Connections

Arduino - Light Dimmer
3V - VCC
GND - GND
Pin 2 (interupt pin 2) - ZC
Pin 1 - PWM

Arduino - HC-05
Pin 10 - RXD
Pin 9 - TXD
GND - GND
3V - VCC

Arduino - RTC
22 (SCL1 pin)  - SCL
23 (SDA1 pin) - SDA
GND - GND
3V - Vin

Arduino - Push Button
Pin 14 (interrupt 14) - top left button pin
GND - 10K resistor - top right button pin
3V - bottom right button pin